author: Bud Poliquin | bpoliquin@syracuse.com
title: Who'd have thunk it: The Mets, equal parts amazin' and magical, are bound for World Series
text: Who'd have thunk it: The Mets, equal parts amazin' and magical, are bound for World Series NLCS Game 4: New York Mets vs. Chicago Cubs The good times are rolling for the New York Mets and those folks who've believed in them for so long. Against pretty big odds (but not all odds), the Amazins are bound for the World Series beginning on Tuesday in Kansas City against the Royals or in Toronto against the Blue Jays. (Elsa/Pool Photo via AP)
